{"tid":1336064,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"安全至上，見機行事","createTime":"2019-07-20T18:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T02:19:01.000Z","uid":78241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a0837ea363271dc9e7b0cc70a0a1db44660dd034","tid":1336064,"uid":78241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:38:36.000Z","msg":"我唔會講咩「武運亨通」，因為呢句有前提。<br />\n<br />\n知道唔啱聽，但希望大家唔好為衝而衝，因為無謂踩隻腳落個已知既陷阱到。<br />\n香港人最叻係靈活變通，希望聽日大家既bewater技能可以再上一點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrG8Zz0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrG8Zz0.jpg&h=2995c100&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n危險區大家要提防。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好留太夜，唔好拖太耐(對峙)，見機行事</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，祝大家萬事平安"},{"pid":"bd042922d27b96d8b8d5fa7f07e2edebd09e98fe","tid":1336064,"uid":191989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:13:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe6da88cfebf9a7227af52fdc787c1e55256908b","tid":1336064,"uid":219216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd042922d27b96d8b8d5fa7f07e2edebd09e98fe","tid":1336064,"uid":191989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:13:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T20:18:24.000Z","msg":"話明見機行事 邊有叫人散"},{"pid":"b4461c2039dcd2c2f2dd405238ce94e89de16083","tid":1336064,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T20:22:40.000Z","msg":"同我一嘢出晒嚟"},{"pid":"3732adf64d83a03244688ad35e3b8610c6002df1","tid":1336064,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T20:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce8a3f229d94ab1779fad24992eb383829198e96","tid":1336064,"uid":267337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:19:01.000Z","msg":"推"}]}